00:24:10.550 --> 00:24:14.560
have this idea that australophitecus has
more ape-like limb proportions, longer

00:24:14.560 --> 00:24:19.570
upper limbs, smaller lower limbs. Based
partly on good old Lucy here, Lucy is

00:24:19.570 --> 00:24:23.860
teeny tiny so this is lower limb to upper
limb. You can pretty much pick your

00:24:23.860 --> 00:24:27.730
favorite measure, it doesn't much matter.
