00:25:48.010 --> 00:25:52.780
side to side, a fully modern human foot
really well adapted for long distance

00:25:52.780 --> 00:25:56.980
travel on the ground. So this isn't really
maybe as different as we would have

00:25:56.980 --> 00:26:00.770
thought a long time...or a number of years
