00:38:11.710 --> 00:38:18.800
reasonably new approach to study in human
evolution and we can understand a lot

00:38:18.800 --> 00:38:25.170
about the evolution of the genus Homo by
looking at life history and by looking at

00:38:25.170 --> 00:38:31.390
modern people. So basically, life history
is more than just looking at the evolution

00:38:31.390 --> 00:38:37.340
of the physical body form. What it is is
looking at how we got to this body form.

00:38:37.340 --> 00:38:42.550
Life history is your tempo and mode of
